text: Aija Kukule (born in Rēzekne 1 October 1956) is a Latvian singer. She received the Great Music Award (Lielā Mūzikas balva), Latvia's highest national music award, in 1993. ==Discography== * Naktsputni [with "Modo"]. Melodija, 1978. * Dzied Aija Kukule [EP]. Melodija, 1980. * Dzied Aija Kukule un "Dzeguzīte". 1985. * Raimonda Paula dziesmas. Melodija, 1985. * Meža gulbji. Mikrofona ieraksti, 1995. * Labākās dziesmas. Baltic Records Group, 2005. ==References== Category:Latvian female singers Category:Living people Category:1956 births Category:People from Rēzekne
title: Aija Kukule
